videos.description: Jarrett Culver feeds Zhaire Smith who explodes to the basket and slams it in against South Carolina.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Culver finds Smith for two-handed jam

videos.description: Justin Gray passes to Niem Stevenson inside the paint and he finishes at the rim with an easy dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Stevenson throws it down for the Red Raiders

videos.description: Justin Minaya's layup is blocked by Texas Tech's Justin Gray but he gets it back and lays it in for a chance at a 3-point play in the first half.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Minaya keeps it alive for hoop

videos.description: Texas Tech's Zhaire Smith gets caught in traffic down low but dishes it to Tommy Hamilton IV who finishes with a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Hamilton hammers it home for Texas Tech

videos.description: Keenan Evans gets past South Carolina's Wesley Myers for a tricky bucket while drawing a foul in the beginning of the second half.
videos.headline: Red Raiders' Evans creates 3-point play

videos.description: The winner of the baby race is completely worn out after reaching the finish line first during a break at the Texas Tech-South Carolina game Saturday.
videos.headline: South Carolina's baby race tires out competitors

videos.description: The Gamecocks use a series of bounce passes before finding Maik Kotsar inside the paint, who makes a nice layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Kotsar scores after beautiful South Carolina passing

videos.description: Keenan Evans hits a big 3-pointer to give the Red Raiders a 1-point lead with less than two minutes left in regulation against South Carolina.
videos.headline: Evans drills 3 to give Texas Tech lead

videos.description: Keenan Evans dribbles to get inside the paint for a tough layup and draws the foul on Wesley Myers.
videos.headline: Evans drives for clutch 3-point play

videos.description: Keenan Evans scores 31 points in No. 14 Texas Tech's 70-63 victory over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Texas Tech fends off South Carolina
